                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6702" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TM-0003</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7810 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风疾知草韧：海洋村民宿战“疫”转危为机</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The strong wind reveals the resilience of the grass: A battle against COVID-19 of Ocean Village B&amp;B Resort, turning crisis into opportunities</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邹蓉，蔡佳静，王澳，宋思旭，华美晨</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南财经政法大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉阳森商业管理有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">民宿行业；组织韧性；可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">B&amp;B industry; organizational resilience; sustainable development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">坐落于武汉市江夏区的海洋村民宿度假酒店，是返乡能人杨驰升着力打造的美丽乡村项目，也是助推海洋村乡村振兴的重要抓手。然而，2020年初新冠肺炎疫情爆发，旅游接待业遭受重创，各大景区和酒店纷纷闭门谢客。海洋村民宿作为武汉民宿业界一颗冉冉升起的新星，在疫情危机之下同样面临着骤然坠落的风险。本案例通过描述海洋村民宿度假酒店的诞生与成长经历，探究了在发展时期、疫情低谷时期以及疫情防控常态化时期，民宿经营团队如何审时度势、储备实力和识别机会，通过控制运营成本、安抚员工情绪、稳定社会关系和丰富产品活动等行动，使得民宿在危机中出现回暖升温的迹象，体现和增强了民宿的组织韧性，为更长远的发展奠定坚实的基础。本案例旨在探讨疫情常态化背景下，小型乡村民宿如何通过组织韧性挺过“危”，走向“机”，也为疫情挑战下的乡村第三产业振兴提供理论参考和经验借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Ocean Village B&amp;B Resort, located in Jiangxia District of Wuhan city, is a program for beautiful countryside built by rural elite, Yang Chisheng as well as a major breakthrough to promote rural revitalization of Ocean Village.However,The outbreak of COVID-19 in early 2020 have hit the tourism hospitality industry seriously,with major scenic spots and hotels closing their doors.Ocean Village Resort B&amp;B,as a rising star in Wuhan B&amp;B industry,was also facing the risk of sudden decline under the epidemic crisis.By introducing the birth of Ocean Village B&amp;B Resort and its growth experience, this case aims to explore the management team how to size up the situation,reserve strength and catch opportunities during the development period,epidemic-outbreak period and epidemic normalized period.Through controlling operating costs,calming employees’ emotions, strengthening social relations and enriching product activities series of actions, management team make the B&amp;B rising up again in the crisis,thus enhance the organizational resilience and lay a solid foundation for long-term development. Therefore,this case will first discuss how small-size B&amp;B can survive in the “crisis” and catch the “opportunity” under the background of epidemic normalization, then provide theoretical support and suggestions for the sustainable development of other B&amp;B.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《旅游企业战略管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织韧性的作用情境及定义；组织韧性的影响因素；组织韧性的构建机制；如何深化组织韧性</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
